
*****
THIS PROJECT USES MULTIPLE LICENCES.
*****

Generally, library sources are licenced under the BSD-2-Clause, while CLI
sources are licenced under the Artisan Software Licence.

Specific files will each have comment blocks at the file heads declaring which
licence applies to them. Consult these as needed.

The full licence terms are included in this repository for reference.
- The Artisan Software Licence can be found at "etc/COPYING.ASL".
- The BSD-2-Clause licence can be found at "etc/COPYING.BSD2C".
